title: TrojanDownloaderWin32Agentcwlb
extract: A Trojan:Win32/Agent is the definition (from Microsoft) of a Trojan downloader, Trojan dropper, or Trojan spy. ... Win32/Agent-trojans very often modify the following subkey in order to accomplish this: HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run.
